{"text_id":240609,"tokens":["Control","la","bility"," of"," the"," heat"," and"," wave"," equations"," and"," their"," finite"," difference"," approximations"," by"," the"," shape"," of"," the"," domain"," is"," a"," problem"," of"," significant"," interest"," in"," control"," theory"," and"," numerical"," analysis","."," In"," this"," work",","," we"," investigate"," how"," the"," control","la","bility"," properties"," of"," these"," equations"," depend"," on"," the"," shape"," of"," the"," domain","."," Our"," key"," idea"," is"," to"," exploit"," the"," fact"," that"," the"," eigenvalues"," of"," the"," Laplace"," operator"," are"," sensitive"," to"," the"," shape"," of"," the"," domain",","," and"," use"," this"," sensitivity"," to"," control"," the"," control","la","bility"," properties"," of"," the"," equations","."," We"," employ"," a"," combination"," of"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," techniques"," to"," study"," the"," control","la","bility"," of"," the"," equations"," and"," their"," finite"," difference"," approximations","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," shape"," of"," the"," domain"," plays"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," determining"," the"," control","la","bility"," of"," the"," equations",","," and"," that"," certain"," domain"," shapes"," can"," lead"," to"," improved"," control","la","bility","."," We"," also"," investigate"," the"," robustness"," of"," our"," results"," to"," numerical"," approximation"," and"," noise","."," The"," problem"," we"," address"," has"," important"," implications"," for"," the"," design"," of"," controllers"," for"," complex"," systems",","," and"," our"," work"," attempts"," to"," solve"," it"," by"," developing"," a"," new"," framework"," for"," controlling"," the"," heat"," and"," wave"," equations"," based"," on"," the"," shape"," of"," the"," domain","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}